  <name>Inkshade PDF</name>
  <summary>Modern PDF reader with annotation and drawing tools</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Inkshade PDF is a modern and intuitive desktop PDF reader featuring advanced
      text selection, powerful search capabilities, and comprehensive annotation tools.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Advanced text selection with word-by-word precision</li>
      <li>Powerful search with navigation between results</li>
      <li>Highlight and annotate text</li>
      <li>Freehand drawing tools</li>
      <li>Dark and light mode themes</li>
      <li>Customizable zoom levels</li>
      <li>Table of contents navigation</li>
      <li>Undo/redo support for annotations</li>
      <li>Save annotations to PDF files</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.github.dafaqboomduck.InkshadePDF.desktop</launchable>

